{"tid":801214,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【最先進科技城市】深圳變澤國停工停課 廣東多地發紅色預警水浸","createTime":"2018-08-31T12:25:58.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-01T12:37:57.000Z","uid":179810,"like":19,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":21,"replies":[{"pid":"4e061a3b26400ab0ee315afbfa961086054a8285","tid":801214,"uid":179810,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-31T12:25:58.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/china/realtime/article/20180830/58623496\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180830%2F58623496&d=kDEuW%2BW1JaXomLAtNExz5%2F755KD0hvcRsprRlRVhNBc%3D&h=1e22f4b5\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180830%2F58623496&h=49d4ac25\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/china/realtime/article/20180830/58623496</a><br />\r\n<br />\r\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20180830/large/1535593906_2019.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20180830%2Flarge%2F1535593906_2019.jpg&h=2f662721&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\r\n<br />\r\n深圳市普遍地區今早落大雨，市氣象局一度發布紅色暴雨預警信號，到早上9時改發黃色預警，預計多處地區仍有大雨，進入緊急防禦狀態，中小學今日全部停課。寶安區及公明區早上上班時間有暴雨，有居民在微博上載圖片，見到部份馬路水浸。<br />\r\n<br />\r\n截至今早8時，深圳市多地累積雨量達特大暴雨，其中龍崗布吉達雨量是415.5mm，雨勢之猛在8月相當罕見！由於寶安松崗橋底積水嚴重，現警力已在現場進行管控即往公明方向已暫時封路，北上司機請注意，前往該路段的車輛繞道而行。<br />\r\n<br />\r\n除了水浸，今早7時許，溪湧金海灘度假村路段發生路塌。而龍崗轄區一處圍牆倒塌壓壞5輛車，所幸未造成人員傷亡。<br />\r\n<br />\r\n另外，截至今日6時46分，廣東新會、深圳、東莞、惠東、陸豐、普寧、惠來暴雨紅色預警信號生效，幼兒園、中小學、中等職業等學校停課。中山三鄉嚴重水浸，多個小區停車場注滿水，多架車輛被浸。<br />\r\n深圳當局凌晨通知本港，深圳水庫在凌晨2:30排洪，港府相關部門包括北區民政事務處，渠務署、警務處和消防處等，採取跟進措施，防止新界地區可能出現水浸。有打鼓嶺居民表示，今早水浸情況並不嚴重。<br />\r\n<br />\r\n綜合報道<br />\r\n<br />\r\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20180830/large/1535593437_abe5.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20180830%2Flarge%2F1535593437_abe5.jpg&h=56334116&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\r\n<br />\r\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20180830/large/1535593755_2cfd.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20180830%2Flarge%2F1535593755_2cfd.jpg&h=714fca14&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\r\n<br />\r\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20180830/large/1535593768_8204.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20180830%2Flarge%2F1535593768_8204.jpg&h=aa15f179&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\r\n<br />\r\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20180830/large/1535593800_bb96.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20180830%2Flarge%2F1535593800_bb96.jpg&h=91df18f1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\r\n<br />\r\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20180830/large/1535593799_c8ea.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20180830%2Flarge%2F1535593799_c8ea.jpg&h=48a9af38&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\r\n<br />\r\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20180830/large/1535593800_ebde.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20180830%2Flarge%2F1535593800_ebde.jpg&h=e0505f76&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\r\n<br />\r\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20180830/large/1535594083_d088.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20180830%2Flarge%2F1535594083_d088.jpg&h=7a99c4bc&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"31a0344cd023c7a037944379953c4f32ff65153f","tid":801214,"uid":25566,"like":0,"dislike":17,"score":-17,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-31T12:27:25.000Z","msg":"咁似香港<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"22695bb6d810427d715920c0f8e2a397c708c894","tid":801214,"uid":179810,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-31T12:30:06.000Z","msg":"【暴雨成災】深圳萬象城變「孤島」 網民：LV手袋快飄出嚟<br />\r\n<br />\r\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20180830/large/1535596286_d54e.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20180830%2Flarge%2F1535596286_d54e.jpg&h=86ae3d1a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\r\n<br />\r\nLV深圳萬象城店外道路嚴重水浸。(互聯網)<br />\r\n<br />\r\n廣東多地自昨日開始出現連續暴雨。鄰近香港的深圳有無數網民將昨日至今早水浸情況上傳微博。其中深圳萬象城周圍道路被出現水浸，車輛要涉水而過。萬象城有如一個「孤島」。有網民拍下LV萬象城店的外圍相，笑言「再等等，LV的包包馬上飄出來了，睡醒後去撈」，留言除了充滿喜感。亦有網民拍下昨日有地區水深及腰的影片。<br />\r\n<br />\r\n網民留言：<br />\r\n<br />\r\n李俊菲：已經下了14個小時的雨，連口氣都沒喘過，深圳已成海了！<br />\r\n<br />\r\nDJ阿聖867：深圳這場雨下的太狠了！布吉火車站對面源豐酒店門口，這些車廢了！<br />\r\n<br />\r\nJolin-姜久莉：深圳的雨已經下了一天一夜了。再等等，LV的包包馬上飄出來了，睡醒後去撈<br />\r\n<br />\r\n番茄炒個土豆：下了一夜的雨 深圳都成了水城了 ​<br />\r\n<br />\r\n巴黎門前的小鐵匠：深圳的雨 一言難盡<br />\r\n<br />\r\n新浪微博"},{"pid":"b5ffb54da9c319be8d8bd29068a6f79f5015f5aa","tid":801214,"uid":179810,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-31T12:31:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://www.881903.com/News_Images/NewsBoss/resize/20180830_20180830-113949.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.881903.com%2FNews_Images%2FNewsBoss%2Fresize%2F20180830_20180830-113949.jpg&h=2d65a9ef&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\r\n<img src=\"http://www.881903.com/News_Images/NewsBoss/resize/20180830_20180830-114031.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.881903.com%2FNews_Images%2FNewsBoss%2Fresize%2F20180830_20180830-114031.jpg&h=4fcfe1da&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\r\n<img src=\"http://www.881903.com/News_Images/NewsBoss/resize/20180830_20180830-114327.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.881903.com%2FNews_Images%2FNewsBoss%2Fresize%2F20180830_20180830-114327.jpg&h=75ec471d&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"d568a186ea231566b934f7925b2f8f00cb973afd","tid":801214,"uid":179810,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-31T12:32:06.000Z","msg":"暴雨襲汕頭 古老平房幾近遭淹沒<br />\r\n<br />\r\n深圳市普遍地區今早落大雨，市氣象局一度發佈紅色暴雨預警信號，預計多處地區仍有大雨，全市進入緊急防禦狀態，中小學今日全部停課。廣東多地發紅色預警。<br />\r\n<br />\r\n22:20 汕頭市潮南區今晚再現暴雨，當地洪水淹沒路面，而昨晚今晨的大雨，已經令到地的古老平方被淹。當地民眾感嘆：「慘慘慘，幾十年一遇的暴雨洪水，竟然5年內出現了兩次！」<br />\r\n<br />\r\n20:00 深圳當局指出，昨晚今晨的暴雨，創1952年以來8月份最大24小時雨量記錄（413毫米），羅湖、福田、龍崗都發出現特大暴雨。消防部門則指出自昨晚8時至今早6時，共出動處理56宗水浸報告，解救被困群眾215人，疏散600多人。<br />\r\n<br />\r\n<br />\r\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20180830/large/1535638979_52db.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20180830%2Flarge%2F1535638979_52db.jpg&h=f2ed5f45&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\r\n汕頭市潮南區的平房，被洪水淹浸。"},{"pid":"6e320c67204ae26e23a7180f3db47e1111642bf0","tid":801214,"uid":55913,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-31T13:14:12.000Z","msg":"又超越香港了！<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"77184b6acee547299eaa1e3606d9587780acb471","tid":801214,"uid":62815,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-31T13:22:10.000Z","msg":"厲害了我d國<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"361df9e7150dc675fa15cc360479cb41bdec6c6a","tid":801214,"uid":30169,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-31T13:24:31.000Z","msg":"好強"},{"pid":"318e41e450796182ba08493a998828d69a9e03b5","tid":801214,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-01T04:07:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"546d961bb78cb341b336e84930e4e2c912514460","tid":801214,"uid":52942,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-01T04:59:34.000Z","msg":"好彩仲有黨<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"80f9abac1